Class CompositeContainer

java.lang.Object
model.containers.CompositeContainerHead
model.containers.CompositeContainer
public class CompositeContainer
extends CompositeContainerHead
CompositeContainer class extends CompositeContainerHead to represent a hierarchical structure of any depth Consists of a value and a key value that describes it.
